Package: hashmyfiles
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0
Description: File integrity scanner and verifier
 HashMyFiles scans files and generates cryptographic hash databases
 (SHA-256, SHA-512, BLAKE3) for integrity verification. Features
 multi-threaded scanning, interactive diff viewer, and export to
 TXT/JSON/CSV formats.
 .
 Created by Jegly.
